+# Before-After Gallery Block — Implementation Plan
+
+## Overview
+
+Build a new `before-after-gallery` block for AEM Edge Delivery Services (XWalk/UE authoring). This is a **P1 HIGH complexity** interactive block used on **SkyriziHCP** and **Rinvoq DTC** (2 pages across 38). It combines a draggable before/after image slider with tab toggles (e.g., Week 16/52 or Adult/Adolescent) and thumbnail navigation for multiple body areas.
+
+## Source Site DOM Analysis
+
+### SkyriziHCP (`skyrizihcp.com/dermatology/psoriasis-efficacy/before-and-after`)
+
+**Gallery wrapper**: `abbv-tabs.risa-tabs-images.abbv-tabs-images` — uses the AEM Tabs component as the outer container.
+
+**Structure**:
+- **Tabs component** (`abbv-tabs.risa-tabs-images`) contains two tab panels: Week 16 and Week 52
+- Each tab panel contains a `.risa-tabs-images__pic-container` with 3 children:
+  1. `.image-compare-slider` → `.abbv-img-slider` (the before/after slider)
+  2. `.columns` → `.abbv-row-container` (before/after labels + patient info)
+  3. `.container` → thumbnail carousel (9 patient thumbnails)
+- **20 total sliders**: 10 per week timepoint (one per patient)
+- Week toggle: `a[href="#week-16"]` / `a[href="#week-52"]` anchor links
+
+**Slider DOM** (`.abbv-img-slider`):
+```html
+<div class="abbv-img-slider" data-slide-direction="horizontal" data-start-point="50%">
+  <img src="patient-illinois-week-16.jpg" alt="After">
+  <div class="img-alt-container" style="width: 50%">
+    <img src="patient-illinois-week-0.jpg" alt="Before">
+  </div>
+  <span class="slider-handle abbv-icon-swap_horiz" style="left: 50%"
+        data-digitaldata="{...analytics JSON...}"></span>
+</div>
+```
+
+**Labels**: "BEFORE | WEEK 0" and "AFTER | WEEK 16" in paragraph elements. "Patient from Illinois" attribution.
+
+**Thumbnails**: 9 patient images per week, horizontal scrollable row. Each thumbnail shows the before image as a clickable preview.
+
+### Rinvoq DTC (`rinvoq.com/atopic-dermatitis/rinvoq-results/eczema-pictures`)
+
+**Gallery wrapper**: `.before-after-video-hero` (hero background container) → `.slider-comparison-container` → `.adults-slider-container`/`.view-adolecents-slider`.
+
+**Structure**:
+- **Toggle buttons**: `.toggle-pictures-slider` container with two links: "View Adult Results" / "View Adolescent (12-17) Results"
+- **Adult section** (`.adults-slider-container.view-adults-slider`): 4 sliders (`.slider1-1` through `.slider1-4`)
+- **Adolescent section** (`.view-adolecents-slider`): separate set of sliders (`.slider2-1`, `.slider2-2`, etc.)
+- **6 total sliders**: 4 adult + 2 adolescent (fewer body areas than SkyriziHCP)
+
+**Thumbnail grid**: `.slider-thumbnails-container` → `.slider-thumbnails.adults` containing 4 thumbnails per group. Each thumbnail has:
+- Thumbnail image with clearance percentage label ("Legs / 75% clearance")
+- Trigger class: `.trigger1-slider1`, `.trigger1-slider2`, etc.
+- Active state: `.border-thumbnails-active` class on `.thumbnail1-1`, etc.
+
+**JavaScript interaction** (`abbvAction.addAction`):
+```js
+abbvAction.addAction('.trigger1-slider1', 'click', [
+  'removeClass|hide-slider-tab|.slider1-1',
+  'addClass|border-thumbnails-active|.thumbnail1-1',
+  'addClass|hide-slider-tab|.slider1-2',
+  'removeClass|border-thumbnails-active|.thumbnail1-2',
+  // ... hide all other sliders, deactivate all other thumbnails
+]);
+```
+
+Pattern: clicking a thumbnail shows that slider (remove `hide-slider-tab`/`d-none`) and hides all others. Thumbnail gets `border-thumbnails-active` class.
+
+**Slider DOM** (identical pattern to SkyriziHCP): `.abbv-img-slider` with `data-slide-direction="horizontal"` and `data-start-point="50%"`.
+
+**Clearance badges**: Each thumbnail shows "75% clearance" or "90% clearance" as overlaid text.
+
+### Key Differences Between Sites
+
+| Feature | SkyriziHCP | Rinvoq DTC |
+|---|---|---|
+| Tab toggle | Week 16 / Week 52 (timepoints) | Adult / Adolescent (age groups) |
+| Patients per tab | 9 (from different US states) | 4 (body areas with clearance %) |
+| Tab implementation | AEM Tabs component (`abbv-tabs`) | Custom toggle links + show/hide |
+| Thumbnail layout | Horizontal scrollable carousel | 2×2 grid with clearance badges |
+| Labels | "BEFORE \| WEEK 0" / "AFTER \| WEEK 16" | Before/After text + clearance % |
+| Patient attribution | "Patient from [State]" + doctor credit | None visible |
+| Thumbnail active state | Visual highlight | `.border-thumbnails-active` class |
+
+## Architecture Decision
+
+**New block `before-after-gallery`** — self-contained, does NOT modify `image-compare`. Reasons:
+- Both source sites compose the gallery from multiple AEM primitives (tabs + image-compare-slider + columns + containers + actions JS); EDS consolidates into a single semantic block
+- The gallery manages tabs, thumbnails, and active image set state internally
+- The slider reuses the proven `--compare-position` CSS pattern from the existing `image-compare` block
+- `image-compare` remains available for standalone single-comparison use (e.g., Venclexta)
+
+## Spec-Aligned Component Model
+
+### Variants (`classes` field)
+| Value | CSS Class | Description | Brand Example |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| — | Default | Tab strip + thumbnail grid + slider | SkyriziHCP (Week 16/52) |
+| `toggle` | `.before-after-gallery-toggle` | Two-state toggle buttons instead of tab strip | Rinvoq DTC (Adult/Adolescent) |
+
+### Component Model Fields
+| Field | Type | Notes |
+|---|---|---|
+| `classes` | select | `toggle` variant |
+| `heading` | text | Gallery heading (e.g., "See Actual Patients Treated With SKYRIZI") |
+| `description` | richtext | Introductory text below heading |
+| `sliderPrompt` | text | Instruction overlay (default: "Click and drag to see results") |
+| `beforeLabelPrefix` | text | Before label prefix (e.g., "BEFORE \| WEEK 0") |
+| `afterLabelPrefix` | text | After label prefix template (e.g., "AFTER \| ") — tab label appended |
+| `anchorId` | text | Deep-link anchor ID |
+| `analyticsId` | text | `data-analytics` on gallery wrapper |
+| `tabs` | model | Tab/toggle items (repeating) |
+| ↳ `tabLabel` | text | Tab button text (e.g., "Week 16", "View Adult Results") |
+| ↳ `openDefault` | boolean | Active tab on load |
+| ↳ `images` | model | Image pairs for this tab (repeating) |
+| ↳↳ `thumbnail` | reference | Thumbnail image for grid navigation |
+| ↳↳ `thumbnailAlt` | text | Thumbnail alt text |
+| ↳↳ `thumbnailLabel` | text | Primary label (e.g., "Legs", "Patient from Illinois") |
+| ↳↳ `thumbnailSubLabel` | text | Secondary label (e.g., "75% clearance", "Dr. Meyer Horn") |
+| ↳↳ `beforeImage` | reference | Before state full image |
+| ↳↳ `beforeAlt` | text | Before image alt (required) |
+| ↳↳ `afterImage` | reference | After state full image |
+| ↳↳ `afterAlt` | text | After image alt (required) |
+
+### Functional Requirements (from source DOM + spec)
+- Tab/toggle navigation switches between complete image sets (timepoints or age groups)
+- Thumbnail grid shows all body areas/patients for the active tab; clicking a thumbnail loads that pair into the main slider
+- Main slider: draggable before/after comparison with CSS `clip-path`/`--compare-position`
+- Slider handle: mouse drag, touch drag, keyboard (ArrowLeft/ArrowRight) — same as existing `image-compare` block
+- ARIA: `role="slider"` on handle, `role="tablist"`/`role="tab"` on tabs, `aria-selected`, `aria-controls`
+- First thumbnail active by default on load
+- Prompt text shown until first drag interaction, then hidden
+- `prefers-reduced-motion`: disable smooth transitions
+- Responsive: thumbnails stack 2-column on mobile; slider full-width
+- All label text authored — zero hardcoded copy in JS
+- Handle icon: CSS `::before` with swap arrows SVG (from `abbv-icon-swap_horiz`)
+
+## File Structure
+
+```
+blocks/before-after-gallery/
+├── before-after-gallery.js          # Tabs + thumbnails + slider orchestration
+├── before-after-gallery.css         # All styles: tabs, thumbnails, slider, responsive
+├── _before-after-gallery.json       # UE component definition, model, filters
+├── block-config.js                  # Empty scaffold
+├── abbvie/                          # Brand override scaffold
+│   ├── _before-after-gallery.css
+│   ├── before-after-gallery.css
+│   └── block-config.js
+├── botox/                           # Brand override scaffold
+│   ├── _before-after-gallery.css
+│   ├── before-after-gallery.css
+│   └── block-config.js
+└── rinvoq/                          # Brand override scaffold
+    ├── _before-after-gallery.css
+    ├── before-after-gallery.css
+    └── block-config.js
+```
+
+## CSS Classes (JS-produced)
+
+```
+before-after-gallery                    (block wrapper)
+before-after-gallery-heading            (h2 heading)
+before-after-gallery-description        (intro richtext)
+before-after-gallery-tabs               (tab bar container)
+before-after-gallery-tab                (individual tab button)
+before-after-gallery-tab.is-active      (active tab state)
+before-after-gallery-content            (active tab's content wrapper)
+before-after-gallery-slider             (main comparison area)
+before-after-gallery-after              (after image layer — full width base)
+before-after-gallery-before             (before image layer — clipped via --compare-position)
+before-after-gallery-handle             (drag handle line + circle)
+before-after-gallery-prompt             (drag instruction overlay text)
+before-after-gallery-labels             (before/after text labels container)
+before-after-gallery-label-before       (before label text)
+before-after-gallery-label-after        (after label text)
+before-after-gallery-attribution        (patient/doctor attribution text)
+before-after-gallery-thumbnails         (thumbnail grid)
+before-after-gallery-thumb              (individual thumbnail card)
+before-after-gallery-thumb.is-active    (selected thumbnail state)
+before-after-gallery-thumb-image        (thumbnail image)
+before-after-gallery-thumb-label        (primary label overlay — "Legs")
+before-after-gallery-thumb-sublabel     (secondary label — "75% clearance")
+```
+
+## Source CSS Reference (from AEM)
+
+Key styles from the source sites to replicate:
+- **Slider handle**: `.slider-handle.abbv-icon-swap_horiz` — white circular handle with swap arrows icon, positioned at `left: var(--compare-position)`
+- **Before image overlay**: `.img-alt-container` — `position: absolute; width: var(--compare-position); overflow: hidden`
+- **Thumbnail active**: `.border-thumbnails-active` — border highlight on selected thumbnail
+- **Tab toggle (Rinvoq)**: `.toggle-pictures-slider` — horizontal flex row of toggle links
+- **Hide/show**: `.hide-slider-tab` / `.d-none` — display toggling for slider panels
+
